=== RadiPanel: Infraction System ===
Contributors: Matthew Gall (iCame), Simon Turp (Swimo)

RadiPanel: Infraction System is an extension of the PHP / MySQL powered RadiPanel system developed by Josh under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 2.0 UK: England & Wales Licence (which can be viewed at http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/2.0/uk/), that allows a system administrator to issue infractions and warnings to members of defined usergroups.

