== IMPORTANT NOTE ==
This product is currently considered to be in ALPHA. This means that under NO circumstances should it be run on any production system unless the user is prepared for frequent updating requiring code edits. The contributors to this product are not responsible for any loss, damage or distruction of data caused by the installation or running of this product. The contributors advise that frequent and full backups should be made before proceeding with installation. You have been warned!
